First set up you [[MIDI]] device in the preferences section of [[Reaper]]. If you are using MAC OS you might need to set up the [[Mac OS:MIDI setup|MAC OS MIDI setup]].


Go to '''Reaper/Preferences.''' Then '''MIDI Devices'''. Enable the MIDI input and output devices in the window that appears (image below).

[[File:Reaper MIDI preferences.png]]


Set the track MIDI input device by clicking on the meter display (image below)





[[File:Reaper track MIDI input.png]]



Set the track output bu clicking on the '''io''' icon and choosing the MIDI output from the '''MIDI Hardware Output''' menu (image below)


[[File:Reaper MID track output.png]]



